{"tid":480554,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"做過私補既你入一入黎","createTime":"2017-11-26T09:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-27T07:10:23.000Z","uid":134989,"like":0,"dislike":17,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9f30c2e98c39646992aa0a8010e57bd8565be3a","tid":480554,"uid":134989,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:31:45.000Z","msg":"本身打算試下 但又驚遇到好L麻煩既家長<br />\n所以去咗做義補一個月 攞下經驗先<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知係唔係因為免費 所以個家長都OK<br />\n反而係個靚妹串77<br />\n第一堂已經話求學不是求分數<br />\n然後不斷串我<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家遇到 d 家長係點<br />\n最麻煩果 d 會唔會對你好高要求<br />\n想要個心理準備<br />\n某大學 year one<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n打算試下小學 我之前個義補靚妹都係小五"},{"pid":"2e73d0984480fb1de28d4c413348e75fc76addeb","tid":480554,"uid":35587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:40:10.000Z","msg":"小5 都咁串就打屌鳩佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2464248368647a571710d9c714d6a8128de79e7","tid":480554,"uid":123731,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:41:44.000Z","msg":"唔會補小學生<br />\n要補都至少中學生<br />\n見過有小學生好煩<br />\n份人工好似包埋要做保母嘅角色咁<br />\n中學生收錢又收多啲<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/25.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce531a52ad6eb8a488fd33fa6dbf169100142d61","tid":480554,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:42:59.000Z","msg":"你on9<br />\n無收錢，仲要收佢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49ac2d995d152e62f04e6a44fb7a8e57cd33f7e2","tid":480554,"uid":18411,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-26T09:43:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你on9<br />\n無收錢，仲要受佢氣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face